halos-mdns-publisher (0.1.1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add multi-label mDNS hostname resolution support
  * Configure nsswitch.conf to use mdns4 instead of mdns4_minimal
  * Install /etc/mdns.allow for .local domain resolution
  * Add libnss-mdns as package dependency
  * Fixes: Device cannot resolve its own mDNS subdomains (e.g., auth.hostname.local)

 -- Hat Labs Ltd <info@hatlabs.fi>  Wed, 25 Dec 2025 14:00:00 +0200

halos-mdns-publisher (0.1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial native systemd service release
  * Replaces container-based halos-mdns-publisher-container
  * Rust implementation with bollard Docker API client
  * Automatic container discovery via halos.subdomain label
  * Graceful degradation when Docker is unavailable

 -- Hat Labs Ltd <info@hatlabs.fi>  Wed, 25 Dec 2025 12:00:00 +0200
